  Step3, "FT-02 (phases.md) + FT-03 (orchestrator.md) + FT-05 (rules.md)", depend on FT-06 completion for content absorption. rules.md absorbs bash/security category from subagent.md
  Step4, FT-01 (SKILL.md), must execute last because file index depends on all other transforms being complete

